9\/01\/16\/pleased-allah-muhammad-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":20786,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I am pleased with Allah, Muhammad, Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever says when he enters the evening, \u2018I am pleased with Allah as a Lord, with Islam as a religion, and with Muhammad as a prophet,\u2019 it will be a duty upon Allah to please him.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35140,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/01\/nifaq-islam-supported\/","url_meta":{"origin":20786,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nifaq: Islam may be supported by sinners and hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty might support this religion by the hands of people who have no share in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 1948 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12401,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2